type: web_research
title: Claude Code Chat Frontend / OpenClaw / Agent SDK Architecture Research (Feb 2026)
source: "Multiple sources: platform.claude.com, code.claude.com, github.com/openclaw/openclaw, blog.modelcontextprotocol.io, docs.anthropic.com"
key_insights[10]: OpenClaw (formerly Clawdbot/Moltbot) is THE open-source middleware for wrapping Claude/LLMs behind Telegram/Discord/Slack/WhatsApp - 135k GitHub stars,"Claude Agent SDK (renamed from Claude Code SDK) provides Python + TypeScript programmatic access with query() async iterator, built-in tools, hooks, subagents, MCP integration","Claude Code headless mode via -p flag supports stream-json output, multi-turn sessions, and tool permissions for building wrappers","MCP Apps standardized Jan 2026 - tools can return interactive HTML UIs in sandboxed iframes, supported by Claude/ChatGPT/VS Code/Goose","Anthropic streaming API uses SSE with content_block_start/delta/stop events, tool_use blocks stream input_json_delta incrementally","OpenClaw architecture: Gateway (WebSocket control plane) + Agent Runtime (Pi RPC) + Skills + Memory, channel abstraction for all messaging platforms",OpenClaw + Claude Code Skill enables MCP-based sub-agent orchestration and context recovery across sessions,"Agent Teams (Feb 2026) = independent Claude Code instances communicating directly, complementing OpenClaw's multi-agent architecture","Branding: Partners can use 'Claude Agent' or 'Powered by Claude' but NOT 'Claude Code' in white-label products","MCP-B embeds MCP servers directly in web pages (~50 lines of code), making websites AI-ready"
findings[10]: "OpenClaw install: npm i -g openclaw@latest, then openclaw onboard wizard","Claude Agent SDK: pip install claude-agent-sdk / npm install @anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk","OpenClaw Gateway runs at ws://127.0.0.1:18789, web dashboard at http://localhost:18789","OpenClaw channels: WhatsApp(Baileys), Telegram(grammY), Slack(Bolt), Discord(discord.js)","Claude Agent SDK supports Bedrock, Vertex AI, Azure AI Foundry as alternative backends","MCP Apps use @modelcontextprotocol/ext-apps package, ui:// scheme for resources",Browser EventSource API doesn't work for Anthropic streaming (POST only) - need fetch with readable stream,OpenClaw Pro/Max subscription usage violates Anthropic ToS - must use API keys,Claude Code plugins ecosystem exists with marketplace at claudemarketplaces.com,Ralph AI plugin converts PRDs to JSON for non-technical users to ship features
recommendations[7]: "For chat-based wrapper: Use OpenClaw for quick multi-platform deployment (Telegram/Discord/Slack/WhatsApp)","For custom web UI: Use Claude Agent SDK (TypeScript) with streaming for real-time responses","For embedding in existing web app: Use MCP Apps with sandboxed iframes for interactive UI","For CI/CD automation: Use claude -p headless mode with stream-json output","For non-technical users: Combine Claude Agent SDK + custom Next.js frontend with simplified UX","For white-label: Use Claude Agent SDK with 'Powered by Claude' branding (not 'Claude Code')","For multi-agent orchestration: OpenClaw + Claude Code Skill for MCP-based sub-agent coordination"
